      • is

        default boolean is(java.lang.Object o)
        Checks whether the object given equals the object wrapped around. If the object given is an IWrapper then the two wrapped objects are checked for equality.
        Parameters:
        o - The object to check
        Returns:
        True if the object equals the object wrapped around or the object wrapped by the object equals the object wrapped around.
